BSmooth-align NEWS
==================

BSmooth-align is now available for download from:

http://rafalab.jhsph.edu/bsmooth/

0.8.0 was the first version uploaded to GitHub.  BSmooth is licensed under the
GPLv3 license.  See `LICENSE' file for details.

Version Release History
=======================

Version 0.8.0 - December 19, 2012
   * Update author's email.
   * Running library unit tests no longer requires Perl module IO::String.
   * Fixed a couple spurious warnings printed in the BtlBio libraries.
   * Fixed a couple issues whereby commands issued to bowtie2 would not use
     proper arguments resulting in warnings.
